\f0\b\fs42 \cf0 THE ANTIDOTE\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs30 \cf0 How do we kill this alligator?\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
GRATITUDE
\f1\b0  \'96 Shifts your eyes from what you lack to what you have. 
\f2\i \'93Give thanks in all circumstances.\'94
\f1\i0  (1 Thessalonians 5:18)\
\ls7\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
CELEBRATION
\f1\b0  \'96 Rejoice with others out loud. It starves envy.\
\ls7\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
CONTENTMENT
\f1\b0  \'96 Paul said, 
\f2\i \'93I have learned to be content whatever the circumstances.\'94
\f1\i0  (Philippians 4:11) Contentment is learned by trusting God\'92s provision.\
\ls7\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
GENEROSITY OF SPIRIT
\f1\b0  \'96 Bless instead of resent. Pray for others\'92 success. Speak life into them.\
